{"tid":1170510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦在內　承受犧牲icon　黃台仰在外　人權　身份認同　達賴路線","createTime":"2019-05-25T04:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T13:33:32.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2c6cbd7dc730b9dec7b61e7663ac82b1d574e1","tid":1170510,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1131777437178580993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1131777437178580993&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=6df1faf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1131777437178580993&h=e882c788\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1131777437178580993</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲講的是從個人出發，這是上一代香港人常見的，但不論梁天琦還是黃台仰做的事有基於香港人這個集體的角度，梁天琦其實講過，他要在內，作為承受犧牲的icon，黃台仰則現在我們看到，是在外，人權路線和著力維持身份認同，類似達賴和熱比婭的世界路線，新世代香港人有些年輕人是有集體在心中。"},{"pid":"cef13db6bd8f80424fbff071042d1820d40885d4","tid":1170510,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}